title: Seahawks-Vikings MNF Recap, Top 5 NFL Coaches (Football 12/3)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap the Seahawks 37-30 victory over the Vikings on Monday Night Football (:10). The guys discuss another primetime loss by Kirk Cousins, a robotic (in multiple ways) Russell Wilson, Dalvin Cook's injury, impact on the playoff picture and much more. Next, the guys react to news that Gardner Minshew is back to being the Jaguars starting QB (30:30), before ranking their Top 5 coaches in the NFL (36:00). Finally, some 5-star comments and questions from Apple Podcasts (58:15).
